    {
      "id": "1288596945740501122",
      "type": "Default",
      "timestamp": "2024-09-26T05:24:12.838+09:00",
      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "Haven't had many opportunities to use this yet, but I really like the QOL of the redesign. Being able to sit on one ghostflame lets you benefit from it multiple times and specialize a bit more, with the obvious best spot to land being bolstering, or just past bolstering if you have forked flame/catch up. If you really want the bonus energy, but are still interested in moving around the wheel at a reasonable pace, you can place a priority on drafting more advance cards, while still benefitting from lighting flames along the way. I'm not entirely convinced hexaghost needs the 4th energy that much, I've had a reasonable number of runs where it doesn't feel that critical due to afterlife and a bevy of very good 0 and 1 cost cards, and hexaghost benefits quite significantly from several non-energy boss relics. Still, I could definitely see decks that take tons of card draw, less afterlife (or afterlife cards they are more interested in playing manually), or more expensive cards that would benefit. Step Through in particular plays well with this since you can light several flames, stop before they get put out by the inferno flame, and then reap the rewards of drawing all those cards while also having plenty of energy to play them. You do have to pick your rare boss card reward before seeing your relic choice, so there's no way to know whether you will be offered a good 4th energy relic or not, but having the option to take this just in case beforehand is still nice if you have ended up in an energy hungry deck.",
      "author": {
        "id": "303064746129752074",
        "name": "kiku_katsumi",
        "discriminator": "0000",
        "nickname": "Kiku",
        "color": null,
        "isBot": false,
        "roles": [],
        "avatarUrl": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/303064746129752074/52a9271c83d647c231c0cfb10f14cf83.png?size=512"
      },
